Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: DNA of MCF-7 cells with WT and NR2F2 KO were extracted using standard Illumina protocals.
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: The MCF-7 cells were maintained in DMEM supplemented with 10% fetal bovinw serum at 37℃ incubator
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: 50,000 sorted cells were washed with cold PBS and suspended in lysis buffer for 10-15 min on ice.  DNA was purified using MinElute PCR Purification Kit (Qiagen). Transposed DNA was amplified using NEB Next High-Fidelity 2X PCR Master Mix and libraries were sequenced on HiSeq 4000, DNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols
Sample_data_processing: Reads were filtered with trimmomatic (version 0.32)., Bowtie version 2.2.4 was used to align the reads against the hg19 reference genome., Samtools 1.9 to remove PCR duplicates, MACS2 to do peak calling on all files
Sample_contact_laboratory: State Key Laboratory of Medical Genomics
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: wig and peak files for each sample
